vourite. But for one to groom a healthy way of eating, you need to enjoy eating these healthy options. That occasional nibble that we have learned to do is a killer when trying to eat right. This is done often without taking cognisance of what we throw into out our mouths. Awareness of what we eats becomes paramount in as bein the first step to eating right. Do not be in a hurry to be perfect but start small and this leads to healthy eating. Peppered Goat Meat | Image Youtube Another step that may be hard is to gradually go for plant-based options or foods that are rich in grains. Whole grains help to increase the blood sugar in slow paces, thereby giving the brain the needed energy to make the day and curbing late-night eating. 